            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Broughtest in.—Of the homeward march. David had thus already discharged kingly functions. (Comp. 1Samuel 8:20; 1Samuel 18:6; 1Samuel 18:13; 1Samuel 18:27; 2Samuel 3:18.)",
        "children": [
